# .semgrepignore — Suppress false-positive findings from static analysis
#
# Rules:
#  - Build artifacts: the dist/ folder is minified 3rd-party vendor code (React,
#    Recharts, Firebase SDK). Issues in minified code are not actionable.
#  - Lock files: package-lock.json pins exact resolved versions. The "variant
#    versions" warning applies to package.json ranges, not the lockfile itself.
#  - FirestoreTest.jsx: development-only debug component, not shipped in prod routes.

# Build output — minified vendor code, not our source
ecotrace/dist/

# Lock files — exact versions are already pinned by the lockfile
cloudrun/nudges/package-lock.json
functions/package-lock.json
